**: Edo period. {{jalink|Thirty-six poets|Q671039|Thirty-six poets and paintings}} written in ink and paper on paper, of which 18 still exist. Dedicated in {{jalink|Kanbun|Q1146228}}9 ({{jalink|1669|Q7602}}). Designated on March 29, 1978 <ref name="Explanation board"/>.
